# M13.2a — Frontend build pipeline.
# Both of these ARE committed (they are the deployed artifact and the
# drift-detection signal). Listed here as a deliberate non-ignore so a
# future "ignore everything generated" sweep does not accidentally drop
# them.
#   - frontend/dist_checksum.txt   IS committed (CI verifies it)
#   - web/index.html               IS committed (it's the deployed page)
# Nothing else under frontend/ is auto-generated, so no new ignore rules
# are required.

